Package: slobr
Title: Read and write files to a SQLite database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Dalgarno", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "seb@poissonconsulting.ca")
Description: A package to run a Shiny app to read and write files to a SQLite database as flobs. A flob is a special type of BLOB type of BLOB that includes the file extension type.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
